defaultPPL is the UK-based music licensing company which licenses recorded music 
defaultto be played in public or broadcast (including certain online 
defaultuses)
default.
default Established in 1934, PPL carries out this role on behalf of over 10,000 record company and 65,000 performer members
default,
default the majority of which are small businesses or sole traders. PPL generated revenue of over £170m in 2012.
default1.2.
