default&#xa0; 
defaultCollective licensing of rights in music and other creative content enables providers of new digital services to reduce transaction costs and invest in and operate their services with the confidence that rights have been cleared. 
defaultIn turn, t
defaulthis also delivers
default efficiencies and 
defaultfair remuneration 
defaultfor creators
default and copyright owners
default and
default,
default ultimately
default,
default a greater range of 
defaultlegitimate 
defaultservices and content for consumers.
