defaultThe BBC has been an advocate of collective licensing 
defaultfor innovative digital services, such as the iPlay
defaulter
default. It has
default, on a number of occasions, been PPL’s first licensee in respect of new forms of 
defaultexploitation, simply due to it being the first to offer those new services and/or to seek collective music rights clearance for them
default. 
